OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to boy, 7, killed
OL,4,Cas he walked on A38 dual carriageway
OL,6,FThe family of a seven-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied after being involved in a
OL,8,Fcollision with two cars on the A38,
OL,9,Fhave called him a "beautiful, loving
OL,10,Fyoung boy".
OL,12,FIsaac Radbourne walked onto the
OL,13,Fnorthbound carriageway at Swinfen,
OL,14,Fnear Lichfield, on Saturday 7 March.
OL,16,FPolice say he got out of his house
OL,17,F"despite preventative and security
OL,18,Fmeasures being in place".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
