CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773162679
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to boy, 7, killed
OL,4,Cas he walked on A38 dual carriageway
OL,6,FHe was involved in a collision with
OL,7,Ftwo other vehicles, a blue Vauxhall
OL,8,FMokka and a white Mercedes.
OL,10,FSpecialist officers have been
OL,11,Fsupporting Isaac's family while
OL,12,Finvestigations into the incident
OL,13,Fcontinue.
OL,15,FIsaac's family said: "Isaac was a
OL,16,Fbeautiful loving young boy who will be
OL,17,Fsorely missed by his parents,
OL,18,Fgrandparents, great grandparents, and
OL,19,Fwider family.
OL,26,@wD@VOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773162679
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to boy, 7, killed
OL,4,Cas he walked on A38 dual carriageway
OL,6,F"Please respect our family and allow
OL,7,Fus time to grieve in privacy."
OL,9,FThe drivers of both vehicles stayed at
OL,10,Fthe scene following the collision and
OL,11,Fcontinue to support the investigation.
OL,13,FStaffordshire Police said: "We
OL,14,Funderstand the impact of this incident
OL,15,Fon the local community and the social
OL,16,Fmedia speculation that has followed.
OL,17,FWe ask that Isaac's family are given
OL,18,Fthe space and privacy needed to grieve
OL,19,Fduring this unprecedented time and
OL,20,Ftheir wishes are respected.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@^O]
